Daughter Got Kidnapped In LA | The Avenger | Action Movie

After their sons death, Matt and his wife move to LA with their daughter Lara. Soon after, his wife is attacked and Lara kidnapped. With only hours to save her, Matt and his ex-special forces buddy Syan embark on a violent rescue mission through LA.

2024.  Stars: Mark Harris, Honor Kneafsey, Deji LaRay
